'''Rashi Bawa''' yɛ Ghanani amanyoni, ɔman ananmusini ne amanyɔkuo New Partriotic Part no mu ni. ɔyɛ Ghana ananmusini a ɔwɔ Nigeria. ɔyɛ Kane Ghana ananmusin a ɔwɔ Saudi Arabia. ɔyɛ kane mmarahyɛ baguani.

== ɔman ananmusifo ==
IWɔ July afe 2017 mu no, ɔmanpanyin Nana Akuffo-Addo paw Rashi Bawa sɛ Ghana ananmusifo wɔ Nigeria. Na ɔka nnipa a wɔn dodoɔ yɛ aduonu mienu a wɔpaw wɔn sɛ wonkɔ som sɛ Ghana ananmusifo wɔ aman ahorɔw so

